Package: morepls
Type: Package
Title: Interpretation tools for Partial Least Squares Regression
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Nicolas", "Robette", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "nicolas.robette@uvsq.fr"))
Imports: pls, ggplot2, ggrepel, rlang
Suggests: plsVarSel, ggforce
Description: Various kinds of plots (observations, variables, correlations, weights, regression coefficients and VIPs) and aids to interpretation (Q2, correlations, redundancies) for partial least squares regressions computed with the 'pls' package.
